       - Update SQLite cache
       - Show success toast: "Item added successfully"
       - Navigate to Manage Inventory Dashboard
     - If Sheets sync **fails**:
       - Show error toast: "Failed to add item. Please try again."
       - Stay on form with data intact
       - User can retry

